# Related ADRs: ADR-015 (JSON-LD & RDF Graph Exports + Visualization Interface)

- **Purpose**: Validate consistency between docs/SSOT/webui-contract.md and webui/graph components to ensure frontend-backend data contract compliance.

- **Required Node Fields**: id (string), label (string), cluster (number)
- **Required Edge Fields**: source (string), target (string), strength (number)
- **Optional Node Fields**: degree, betweenness, eigenvector (numbers)
- **Optional Edge Fields**: rerank, yes (numbers/booleans)

- **File Path Validation**: WebUI loads same file path defined in SSOT (exports/graph_latest.json)
- **Type Consistency**: TypeScript interfaces match SSOT schema definitions
- **Data Loading**: useGraphData hook properly handles SSOT-defined file format
- **Error Handling**: Components gracefully handle missing/invalid data per contract

- **Validation**: Run `make webui` and verify data loads without type errors or missing field warnings.